.DT
auto_mail
Disk World creator help
auto_mail

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
auto_mail -  Allows people to send mail automaticly from the player in question.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int auto_mail(string to,
string from,
string sub,
string cc,
string body,
int send_inter,
string only_to,
int flag)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^to%^RESET%^ - who the mail is to
%^BOLD%^from%^RESET%^ - who the mail is from
%^BOLD%^cc%^RESET%^ - the people to carbon copy
%^BOLD%^body%^RESET%^ - the body of the message
%^BOLD%^send_inter%^RESET%^ - should be send it ove the inter mud system?
%^BOLD%^only_to%^RESET%^ - ignore the cc fields
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the same value as do_mail_message does, 0 on failure
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/auto_mailer.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Allows people to send mail automaticly from the player in question.
Thus allows mail to be sent on someone being promoted to creator
and stuff.
.EP

